OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,FA third Reform candidate has stood
OL,7,Fdown in the Pen-y-Bont Bro Morgannwg
OL,8,Fconstituency ahead of May's Senedd
OL,9,FElection.
OL,11,FReform UK confirmed Cllr Derek Roberts
OL,12,Fis the latest candidate to stand down
OL,13,Fwithin a week, citing "personal
OL,14,Freasons".
OL,16,FThe party's sixth candidate, Owain
OL,17,FClatworthy, also announced he would
OL,18,Fleave in protest against "poor
OL,19,Finternal decision making, lack of
OL,20,Fdiscipline and serious concerns around
OL,21,Fcandidate selection".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
