OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,FCorey Edwards, the first candidate on
OL,7,Fthe constituency list, stood down
OL,8,Fafter a photo emerged of him appearing
OL,9,Fto do a Nazi salute. In a statement to
OL,10,FITV News, Corey Edwards said the photo
OL,11,Fhad been "misinterpreted", while
OL,12,Facknowledging he had made "mistakes."
OL,14,FAll the parties have until 9th April
OL,15,Fto nominate their candidates for May's
OL,16,Felection.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
