OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,FMeanwhile, two Plaid Cymru candidates
OL,7,Fhave come under fire over social media
OL,8,Fposts. The posts on X, formerly
OL,9,FTwitter, and BlueSky were unearthed by
OL,10,FReform UK.
OL,12,FAmong the posts, Plaid Cymru's
OL,13,Fcandidate for Gwynedd Maldwyn, Elin
OL,14,FHywel, appears to describe Cardiff as
OL,15,Fthe "most unappealing city in the
OL,16,Fworld". She also appears to say Wales
OL,17,Fis the "racist capital" of the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
