PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775423488
OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,FA second candidate, Vivek Thuppil, who
OL,7,Fis a Plaid Cymru candidate in Bangor
OL,8,FConwy Mon, is accused of describing
OL,9,FWinston Churchill as a "genocidal
OL,10,Ffascist".
OL,12,FIn a post on BlueSky, Mr Thuppil also
OL,13,Fsays, "Israel is a terrorist state.
OL,14,FAny support for Israel should be
OL,15,Flegally proscribed like for any other
OL,16,Fterrorist entity."
OL,18,FReform UK said: "These quotes are not
OL,19,Fsome misguided musings of a teenager,
OL,20,Fbut are the sincerely held beliefs of
OL,21,Fsomeone who should know better.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
