PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775423488
OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,F"Winston Churchill was one of the
OL,7,Fgreatest leaders in our history.
OL,8,FSadly, this Churchill-hatred is all
OL,9,Ftoo common in some sections of Plaid
OL,10,Fand the hard-left."
OL,12,FIt comes as Neil Roberts, who was
OL,13,Ffourth on the Plaid Cymru list for
OL,14,FCaerdydd Penarth, stepped down after
OL,15,Fan offensive tweet was uncovered.
OL,17,FThe messages, which ITV News has
OL,18,Fchosen not to publish in full, were
OL,19,Fpart of an exchange on the social
OL,20,Fmedia platform Twitter (now X) in 2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
