PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775423488
OL,3,CThree Reform candidates step down in
OL,4,Cone constituency
OL,6,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson hit back at
OL,7,Fthe most recent allegations, saying:
OL,8,F"Reform are desperately deflecting
OL,9,Ffrom their shambolic campaign, which
OL,10,Fhas seen four candidates drop out in
OL,11,Fone week - including one candidate who
OL,12,Fappeared in an image where they
OL,13,Fappeared to show a Nazi salute.
OL,15,F"This is a party mired in controversy,
OL,16,Flacking judgment, and unfit to
OL,17,Frepresent the people of Wales." The
OL,18,Fparty confirmed both would remain
OL,19,Fmembers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
